Privacy Policy for Sariq Bola Courier 

Last Updated: 05.12.2023

1. Overview

Thank you for choosing Sariq Bola Courier App (the "App"), developed by yusufjoncool@gmail.com. This Privacy Policy is designed to inform you about the types of information we may collect, how we use that information, and the choices you have regarding your personal information. By using the App, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.

2. Information We Collect

2.1 Location Information:
The App collects and transmits your device's precise location information in real-time. This data is essential for providing accurate courier services and improving the overall user experience. The location information is only collected when the App is in background mode and actively running.

2.2 Personal Information:
In the course of using the App, you may be required to provide personal information such as your phone number for courier services.


3. How We Use Your Information

3.1 Providing Courier Services:
We use your location information to provide accurate and efficient courier services. Your personal information is used to facilitate communication between users and for the overall functionality of the App.

3.2 Communications:
We may use your contact information to send you important updates, notifications, and information related to the App and its services.

4. Data Security

We take appropriate measures to safeguard your personal information and ensure data security. However, please be aware that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee the absolute security of your data.

5. Third-Party Services

The App may integrate with third-party services or link to external websites. Please note that these services have their own privacy policies, and we are not responsible for their practices. We recommend reviewing the privacy policies of these third-party services.

6. Changes to the Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for legal and regulatory reasons. We will notify users of any material changes through the App or other means.

7. Contact Us

If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy or the handling of your personal information, please contact us at yusufjoncool@gmail.com.

8. Consent

By using the Sariq Bola Courier App, you consent to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.

Thank you for trusting Sariq Bola Courier App.
